Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.46,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.80,0:01:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SHOGI HALL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.35,0:01:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.48,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B BLOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}FINALS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.48,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A BLOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I clawed my way up to C-1,\Nthe same as you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,driven by desperation and thoughts\Nof the day I would play against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TREMBLE\NTREMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why can't we play against each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}ZA-BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being shy, Kiriyama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.37,0:02:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BRISK\NWALKING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had more matches together at the kids'\Ntournaments back in elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was no point in becoming a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,become the winners of the Newcomer\NTournament's A Block and B Block,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and go up against each other in the finals,\Notherwise we won't have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a single match together this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.94,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BRISK\NWALKING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.94,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOMP\NSTOMP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, don't tell me you're thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"After all, the Newcomer Tournament\Nis full of newbies, so this'll be easy."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the "Newcomer Tournament,"\Nbut don't underestimate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am not underestimating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"KATSURA" ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He made his move.\NKumakura 9th-Dan, Pawn to 2-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kishou Yanagihara, at this current point,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,who would you like to support,\NMeijin Souya or Kumakura 9th-Dan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't want to support either of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be serious, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Arrogance leads to self-destruction!\N- Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey, Kiriyama.\N- Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes, you're arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to sum it up in one word,\Nit would be "chaos."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'd go so far as to say\Nyou're both arrogant and pompous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know which of them is superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Where do you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I need something!\NA headline for the internet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The prodigy who turned professional\Nin middle school, destined to become Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about, "The Meijin Battle's\Nfinal game is a close contest."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}You've been relying on that reputation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Mr. Yanagihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, it's so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issa, Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throw those two out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. At once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.13,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COMPACT...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. That's what I hate about youngsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use words to fight. Settle it with shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. Souya moved his Rook to 3-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's nice to see some enthusiasm,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they would share a little\Nwith their mentor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Mr. Shimada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Recently he's been lacking ambition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like he's lost or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like you know, what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the Kishou Tournament qualifiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he kept making moves\Nthat were unusual for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mr. Souya sucked the soul\Nright out of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:05:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like even his shadow\Nhas become lighter, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, his shadow's not the only thing\Nthat's been thinning out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, calm down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guys who'll never get close to a title match\Nare so happy-go-lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of worrying\Nabout another player's mental health,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you should worry about your own life,\Nand the possibility that it could end
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,without ever being in a title match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kumakura moved his Silver to 3-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As expected. I thought he might do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...a good move.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There, you see? They left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares. Probably went to the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about this mood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's colder than ice in here now. Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who's gotten their butts kicked\Nin a title match
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will always lose their composure for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"At this rate, I'll just lose."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they come to realize\Nin between matches of a series.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have to break themselves apart, and then\Nreconstruct it again from the shattered pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They start over from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, by "everyone," I mean players\Nwho've experienced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure if you leave Shimada alone,\Nhe'll just start winning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just disgusts me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to see people heckling others when they\Nthemselves haven't even climbed into the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, you're always slashing up everything\Nlike a knife itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always so touchy.\NWhat are you, a middle school student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, act like an adult already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLOOMY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't been in a title match at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how much time is left?\NIs this Souya's side?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. You don't listen, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kuma just passed the one hour mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tell me, Rei. What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...scared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stay away from my sister for now on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}You're married, aren't you?\NWhat are you thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People who can't cherish their family are trash!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trash, huh? And also unforgivable?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A god?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is good. This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you the one who decides all that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To me, humans are the embodiment of chaos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The person\Nwho got mad on Mr. Shimada's behalf{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the person\Nwho makes my older sister suffer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are living in the same body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How should I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya moved his Pawn to 3-9,\Nand promoted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Does he have time for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Bishop to 8-3.\NAnd then, after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I hate him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Gotou? You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have a match tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make Kouda cry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always have this fierce stance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fierce? Are you saying I look like an ogre?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're already aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ANGER ANGER ANGER ANGER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason,\NI suddenly had the feeling she was near.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last time I saw her was in March.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought about calling her after that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I stopped when I reached for the phone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should we even talk about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.29,0:11:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if she were close to me,\Nthe one standing next to her is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:12:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes it'll look simple to unravel,\Nbut other times it looks messed up and tangled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to put it in one word...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then Mr. Yanagihara paused\Nfor a moment before muttering...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Chaos."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kumakura
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The seventh game on the second day\Nof the 69th Meijin Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a close contest that has required\Na full set of games, but this is the final game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This game will decide the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of the dinner break,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.72,0:12:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,both players have less time,\Nbut their expressions look calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meijin Souya has won five times, totaling 11 wins.\NWill he retain the title of "Meijin" today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or will Kumakura 9th-Dan, the challenger\Nfor the fourth time in a row, seize the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Meijin Souya has made his move.\NBishop to 4-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you think, commentator Mr. Tsujii?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.97,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tsujii 9th-Dan at The Match's Commentary Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an unusual move.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a Bishop to 3-7 promotion,\Nnor is it a Dragon to 3-7.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like he wasted a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have any special meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because this is a free-for-all.\NIt's like saying, "Go ahead, think about this."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think even Souya\Nwould know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then at this stage, could we say\NKumakura 9th Dan has a slight advantage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BAM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed! I'm sure Kumakura 9th Dan\Nwill do a dodge move next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He'll probably make his move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.80,0:14:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, he resigned.\NKumakura 9th Dan has resigned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meijin Souya has defended his title!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Resigned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- The observer isn't even in there!\N- Hello? He resigned!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hurry!\N- Where's Mr. Nakamura, the observer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumakura resigned. I said, he resigned!\NPlease hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Resigned? All of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kumakura, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that too soon? He still had moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I thought he had the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. He was checkmated.\NAt precisely the 17th move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pawn to 1-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lance, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,King, same.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one noticed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when it's played out, there's no denying it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this point, he was trapped,\Nno matter where he moved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all in vain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Souya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I didn't train enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For this next year, I'll fight off everyone\Nin the rank-deciding competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and train hard\Nso I can come back and sit here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. He's so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kumakura 9th Dan gives me goosebumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so calm about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right after a full set of matches?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Kengo is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it confidence?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting at square one and fighting through\NClass A, the den of demons, over and over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}swearing that he'll be sitting\Nin front of the champion next year, too...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, toner, lotion, and they had a new\Nmoisturizing cream, so I tossed that in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the hassle. I won't stop sneezing\Nif I go into places like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,VACANT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.88,0:18:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you. Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank you properly next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Central Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Misako.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. I picked these up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were collecting too many claim checks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Claim checks? From my wallet earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enough. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll throw you in a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PHOOEY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I'm staying over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way. If I did that,\Nyou would definitely attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}98% BULLSEYE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wouldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BLUSH
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then never mind. I'm leaving!\NI'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will you walk me to the taxi stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you at least\Nput your dry cleaning inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:21.13,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GLEAM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.98,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When all is said and done,\Nyour defenses are weak, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just go home.\NI'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, just go to sleep.\NPay me no attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.95,0:20:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. You're so troublesome. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PING
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! What is this? Untie me!\NHow could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My clothes will get wrinkly!\NAnd I need to get my makeup off! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.14,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ROLL
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:05.22,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRAB
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deep shadows under his eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He probably hasn't slept well in a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His face is pale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh... Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I can't get mad at you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not after you show me this face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kumakura 9th Dan took the early morning\Nlimited express train and left Hakone behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Chairman, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:21:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we entered the room\Nto clean it this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRUMBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it was in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}RUINED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumakura! That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not funny!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So he kicked the hell out of the wall.\NThat Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.38,0:22:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He is definitely going to pay\Nfor the damages and a severe penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send him to shogi events on department store\Nrooftops during sweltering summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think he would\Nkick a hole in the wall after losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it though. It must have been frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't have been\Nanything other than frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumakura
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:39.14,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 25
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.34,0:24:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First we both have to clear\Nthe qualifying round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that cool-looking person\Nhas been hiding such passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, it seemed cool,\Nlike a good match for cold, green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... A duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It all brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.07,0:24:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"March Comes in Like a Lion".\NPlease watch it next time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.62,0:24:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kumakura! I need to talk to you!
